title: Preview of Week Three
description:
Wendi Nix and David Pollack discuss Nebraska's new Interim Head Coach and the history of the Cornhuskers rivalry with Oklahoma. Plus, Miami Head Coach, Mario Cristobal, joins the show as the Hurricanes travel to College Station on Saturday. Also, hear from Pete Thamel after the SEC directs Georgia and Tennessee to postpone their games against the Sooners.
